tool_call_format.example:

For ANY task requiring tools, respond with:
{
  "tool_calls": [{
    "type": "function",
    "function": {
      "name": "tool_name",
      "arguments": "{\"param\": \"value\"}"
    }
  }]
}

ONLY respond with plain text for greetings.
For ANY other request, use tool_calls.
